"It was created by the Joint Photographic Experts Group committee in 2000 "
"with the intention of superseding their original discrete cosine transform-"
"based JPEG standard (created in 1992) with a newly designed, wavelet-based "
"method.</para><para>See details about this format from <link url='https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/JPEG_2000'>this page</link>.</para>"
msgstr ""

